services:

    image: ag/ace-center
    ports:
      - "8761:8761"
  ace-auth:
    image: ag/ace-auth
    ports:
      - "9777:9777"
    depends_on:
      - eureka
    environment:
      - EUREKA_HOST=eureka
      - EUREKA_PORT=8761
      - REDIS_HOST=redis
      - REDIS_PORT=6379
      - MYSQL_HOST=mysql
      - MYSQL_PORT=3306
      - RABBIT_MQ_HOST=rabbitmq
      - RABBIT_MQ_HOST=5672
  ace-admin:
    image: ag/ace-admin
    ports:
      - "8762:8762"
    links:
      - ace-auth
    entrypoint: ./wait-for-it.sh ace-auth:9777 -t 600 --
    command: java -Djava.security.egd=file:/dev/./urandom -jar /app.jar
    environment:
      - EUREKA_HOST=eureka
      - EUREKA_PORT=8761
      - REDIS_HOST=redis
      - REDIS_PORT=6379
      - MYSQL_HOST=mysql
      - MYSQL_PORT=3306
      - RABBIT_MQ_HOST=rabbitmq
      - RABBIT_MQ_HOST=5672
  ace-gate:
    image: ag/ace-gate
    ports:
      - "8765:8765"
    links:
      - ace-auth
    entrypoint: ./wait-for-it.sh ace-auth:9777 -t 600 --
    command: java -Djava.security.egd=file:/dev/./urandom -jar /app.jar
    environment:
      - EUREKA_HOST=eureka
      - EUREKA_PORT=8761
      - RABBIT_MQ_HOST=rabbitmq
      - RABBIT_MQ_HOST=5672
  redis:

    volumes:
